  "title": "游中山金钟水库打卡水杉林",
  "summary": "中山金钟水库位于广东省中山市南区街道新安村，总占地面积120公顷，其中水面面积35公顷。2022年新建了金钟湖 […]",
  "content": "<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025122014154999.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1001\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025122014155422.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1001\"></p>\n<p>中山金钟水库位于广东省中山市南区街道新安村，总占地面积120公顷，其中水面面积35公顷。2022年新建了金钟湖公园，穿过公园可到达水库。水库岸线自然曲折，水质常年保持优良标准，东南部存有大面积湿地沼泽地貌，形成水鸟栖息繁殖的生态环境。沿湖12公里环湖步道贯穿次生马尾松林、大叶相思林及粉丹竹林等乡土植被群，还有网红水杉林，每年11月下旬-12月是最佳观赏时间。珠海中山有很多观赏水杉的地方，今年选择金钟水库。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025122014155236.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1001\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/202512201415364.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1001\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025122014155086.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1001\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025122014155163.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1001\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025122014153719.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1001\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025122014155126.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1001\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025122014155175.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1001\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025122014153849.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1001\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025122014155243.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1001\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025122014155335.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1001\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025122014155377.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1001\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025122014155027.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1001\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025122014155433.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1001\"></p>\n<p>By 徕卡 D-LUX8</p>",
